 # Strategizer Reasoning
 
 The strategizer will append its execution reasoning here.
+
+## Iteration 1 - startup and source packet design
+
+- Read `GOAL.md`, `state.json`, `HISTORY-OF-REPORT-SUMMARIES.md`,
