./missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-03.md:31:- "Formulate the hypothetical minimal blowup object" makes it sound as if the object is available once a space is chosen. In reality, this step may already require a profile decomposition, nonlinear perturbation theory, stability under the chosen topology, and a sharp threshold definition compatible with Navier-Stokes scaling.
