./runtime/logs/codex-patlas-beyond-de-giorgi-run-001-attacker-01.log:725:./runtime/logs/codex-patlas-beyond-de-giorgi-run-001-planner.log:1018:/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/vasseur-pressure/steps/step-002/explorations/exploration-002/REPORT-SUMMARY.md:39:All three branches (2A interpolation, 2B BMO/duality, 2C atomic) hit the same wall: the De Giorgi energy provides ∇u ∈ L^2, but improving β to 3/2 requires ∇u ∈ L^3 (W^{1,3} threshold). Besov number computation: W^{1,2} has number -1/2, W^{1,3} has number 0. Non-embedding confirmed. [COMPUTED]
