+- `library/factual/exact-rewrite-obstruction-audit/suitable-weak-leray-hopf-with-lei-is-the-fixed-solution-class.md`
+
+## Output Requirements
+
+Write:
+
+- `REPORT.md`
+- `REPORT-SUMMARY.md`
+
+Keep the conclusion narrow. If the local record is too thin to support a
+single-theorem viability claim, that thinness is part of the result.
