+- Key takeaway:
+  `\dot H^{1/2}` looks cleaner than `BMO^{-1}` on Hilbert-space compactness
+  language, but the local record still does not give one frozen extraction
+  package or one single missing theorem; `BMO^{-1}` should be excluded up
